@c EN
If @var{bit} is true, sets @var{index}-th bit of an exact integer @var{n}.
If @var{bit} is false, resets @var{index}-th bit of an exact integer @var{n}.
@c JP
@var{bit}が真の値なら、整数@var{n}の@var{index}ビット目をセットした数値を
